```

## Composable Mocking

```ts
vi.mock("@/composables/useAuth", () => ({
  useAuth: () => ({
    user: ref({ name: "Test" }),
    isAuthenticated: ref(true),
    logout: vi.fn(),
  }),
}));
```

## Conventions

- Vitest as test runner
- `@vue/test-utils` for mount and queries
- `mount` for integration, `shallowMount` for unit
- `@pinia/testing` for store mocking
- Global stubs for Teleport and Transition
- `vi.mock` for external composables
- Always `await` on `trigger` and `setValue`
